ry odd that I am three times older than you. That is all that I am stating. And I am 666. And at this moment both of us align with 666</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>With Heart,</p><p><br /></p><p>.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>wendy.Smith2008 <wendy.Smith2008@protonmail.com></p><p><br /></p><p>Sun, Nov 1, 2020, 11:33â€¯PM</p><p><br /></p><p>to Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Oh Wendell</p><p><br /></p><p>I dont know if ill ever get to meet you in this life I hope i can but Australia is so far away.</p><p><br /></p><p>Im going back to school on Monday how should i start teaching what issues are the most important?</p><p><br /></p><p>Age is just a number that grown ups use to control children. It doesnt mean anything. Im sure we wont age in Heaven.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Forever yours</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendy</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>â€â€â€â€â€â€â€ Original Message â€â€â€â€â€â€â€</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p><br /></p><p>Sun, Nov 1, 2020, 11:38â€¯PM</p><p><br /></p><p>to wendy.Smith2008</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Dear Wendy, you will get to meet me in life if you work hard for it.</p><p><br /></p><p>As for issues that are most important, stand up for the little guy. Be a shining example for good even though bad continues to win.</p><p><br /></p><p>Age is just a number. I am glad that you see that. I hope that I can spend my life encouraging you to do the right thing.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Conversation opened. 5 messages. All messages read.</p><p><br /></p><p>Skip to content</p><p><br /></p><p>Using Gmail with screen readers</p><p><br /></p><p>label:wendy-rip Remember that philosophy is life. I am interested in your life. I intend to be your mentor now untilÂ </p><p><br /></p><p>2 of 2</p><p><br /></p><p>Career Suggestions</p><p><br /></p><p>W